 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王維基日產10萬個 （得整100萬個既原料）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科學園3月頭開工 日產10萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPoly 重用口罩測試階段 唔防病毒🦠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口罩價格會越來越貴 定回落？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:56:44.000Z","msg":"計香港製造嚟講<br />\n其實材料係一個大問題<br />\n中國自己都唔夠<br />\n佢唔輸出材料<br />\n短期內有幾多地方可以畀你大量購買材料？<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n中國年產量佔咗全球5成<br />\n日產量最高係2000萬個<br />\n我當全球加埋一齊推高生產量<br />\n一日畀你整夠1億個口罩？<br />\n就算當各國產量夠用<br />\n可以反輸出輸出<br />\n各地市場淨係谷畀中國都食晒啦<br />\n<br />\n而家所謂返大貨都係食全球存貨嘅老本<br />\n所以疫情一日未受控<br />\n口罩只會越嚟越渴市<br />\n<br />\n我覺得短期內個價格會穩住<br />\n因為新年前後大家喺各國搜羅返嚟嘅貨到咗香港<br />\n但如果一個月之後疫情重未受控<br />\n我唔知會升到點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a027afef3f906a61c8cfcb1fef4c9c102b04190","tid":1881754,"uid":2556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T23:20:12.000Z","msg":"買緊十幾蚊一隻vfe口罩 <br />\n跟本無得揀。要番工"},{"pid":"f783814e87414417b3de1b7951d0363dd71aeaa8","tid":1881754,"uid":75953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a9e68a221b2f1724dd8393e7be3d81e9acf0410","tid":1881754,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"工賊會話可以日產10萬個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王維基日產10萬個 （得整100萬個既原料）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科學園3月頭開工 日產10萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPoly 重用口罩測試階段 唔防病毒🦠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/